---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import json from '../../dictionaries/data.json'
---

<Layout title="Nick Golitsyn | Portfolio">
	<main class="max-w-screen-xl mx-8" id="home">
		<div class="h-96 flex justify-center items-end">
			<div class="mb-12">
				<h1 class="text-4xl text-center font-semibold">Hello. I am Nick,</h1>
				<h1 class="text-center text-3xl font-medium">A Frontend Web Developer.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div>
			<h2 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2" id="about">About</h2>
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
				<p class="text-gray-500">
					Iâ€™m a 21 year old front-end web developer, with a passion for creating captivating and user-friendly websites. My journey began with college, personal projects and freelance work, and over the years, I have learned to constantly refine my skills and stay current with the latest technologies. Fluent in both English and Russian, I completed a 4-year diploma in web development at IThub College (Moscow) in June 2023, which has equipped me with a solid foundation in programming languages and best practices. In January I completed a 10-week data analysis bootcamp at Cambridge Spark.
				</p>
				<p class="text-gray-500">
					While currently based in Norfolk, UK, I am open to relocation for an opportunity that aligns with my career aspirations. I am excited about joining a forward-thinking team where I can contribute my skills and continue to, embark on continuous learning, and advance in my professional journey. With my dedication and education, I am confident in thriving as a web developer and making a valuable contribution to any team.	
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="mt-10">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">Skills</h2>
			<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
				{json.skills.map((item) => (
					<p class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 text-sm px-3 py-1 border border-gray-300 rounded-sm">{item}</p>
				))}
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="mt-10">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">Education</h2>
			{json.education.map((item) => (
				<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-2 md:gap-5 mb-5">
					<div>
						<p class="w-max text-gray-500">{item.date}</p>
					</div>
					<div> 
						<h3 class="font-medium mb-1">{item.title}</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-500">{item.description}</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			))}
		</div>
		<div class="mt-10">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2">Experience</h2>
			{json.experience.map((item) => (
				<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-2 md:gap-5 mb-5">
					<div>
						<p class="w-max text-gray-500">{item.date}</p>
					</div>
					<div> 
						<h3 class="font-medium mb-1">{item.title}</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-500">{item.description}</p>
						<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-3">
							{item.stack.map((stackItem) => (
								<p class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 text-sm px-3 py-1 border border-gray-300 rounded-sm">{stackItem}</p>
							))}
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			))}
		</div>
		<div class="mt-10">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-medium mb-2" id="projects">Projects</h2>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
				{json.projects.map((item) => (
					<div class="w-full bg-slate-100 border border-gray-300 rounded-md px-5 py-4 flex flex-col gap-2">
						<div class="flex justify-between">
							<h3>{item.title}</h3>
							<div class="flex gap-4">
								<a href={item.git} target="_blank">
									<img class="max-h-6 h-6 max-w-6" src="/github.svg" alt="github logo" />
								</a>
								<a href={item.url} target="_blank">
									<img class="max-h-6 h-6 max-w-6" src="/url.svg" alt="github logo" />
								</a>
							</div>
						</div>
						<p class="text-gray-500">{item.description}</p>
					</div>
				))}
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>